'''Tensori no Mikoto''' (天曽利命) is considered the [[Oyagami|ancestral deity]] of the [[Hayato|Hayato tribe]]<ref name="A109 Tensori no Mikoto">{{Cite web |language=ja |title=A109 天曽利命 |url=https://www.his-trip.info/keizu/entry46.html |website=www.his-trip.info |access-date=2023-12-14}}</ref>,<ref name="sakura.ne.jp">{{Cite web |title=�v�Ď��l |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319134404/http://ek1010.sakura.ne.jp/1234-7-41.html |website=web.archive.org |date=2016-03-19 |access-date=2024-01-06}}</ref>,<ref name="mimizun">{{Cite web |title=【ﾑｰﾀﾞﾝ】李氏朝鮮VS琉球王国7【ﾕﾀ】 |url=https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:27J1abZ5nb0J:mimizun.com/log/2ch/korea/1347841276/ |website=webcache.googleusercontent.com |access-date=2024-01-06}}</ref>,<ref>{{Cite book|language=zh-TW|first=Toshio|last=Hōga|author2=宝賀寿男|title=古代氏族系譜集成|publisher=古代氏族研究会|date=1986|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EL0nAAAAYAAJ&newbks=0&printsec=frontcover&dq=%22%E5%A4%A9%E6%9B%BD%E5%88%A9%E5%91%BD%22&q=%22%E5%A4%A9%E6%9B%BD%E5%88%A9%E5%91%BD%22&hl=en}}</ref>,<ref>[https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/books/R100000002-I000002274014 古代豪族系図集覧]</ref>.
